=== 招聘信息 ===
 
 公司名称:北京铿腾电子科技有限公司 
 招聘职位:AMS CM Software Engineer[急聘]  
 截至日期:2005-11-22  
 最低学历:硕士  
 招聘人数:人 
 工作地点: 北京
 简历投递处: http://www.jobmm.com/cadence/Kuntai_job.asp  
 
岗位描述:  
Job Description:
-Candidate will be in charged of handling the Configuration Management of 
 some Simulator and Simulator interface products. 
-Candidate will create and maintain automated daily build,integrate, package,
 run automated testing,and maintain web based reporting systems on multiple 
 Unix platforms. 
-Candidate will help create standard release packages. 
-Candidate will need to be able to fix process related issues independently. 
-Candidate will work with local and international teams. 
-Candidate will be involved in creation of CM process documentation.
-Candidate will also involved in coding of AMS simulator development 
 
 
相关要求: 
Required
-BS in Computer Science or similar level of expertise with at least 2 years 
 of working experience.
-Good understanding of Makefile, gnumake.
-Good understanding of C/C++ compilers, compiler flags.
-Coding experience with C/C++ under Linux or UNIX
-Good communication in English 
-Experience on Linux/Unix platforms 
-Proficient in scripting languages like Perl, sh/csh, tcl
-Independent and hands off personality； able to work with minimal 
 instructions and supervisions.
Preferred:
-Good understanding of version control systems, clearcase
-Web Server installation and simple web design experience
-Experience in creating automated process 
  
